ene mellom oss og n\u00e6ringen. En annen ting er at vi h\u00e5per \u00e5 bli mer attraktive for folk i hele regionen som vil utdanne seg innen akvakultur, sier Asgeir Johansen, fagansvarlig ved Fr\u00f8ya vgs.", "I dag g\u00e5r 22 elever p\u00e5 VG1-linja naturbruk, mens fem elever g\u00e5r p\u00e5 VG2-linja akvakultur. Neste \u00e5r har imidlertid 15 elever meldt seg p\u00e5 den nevnte VG2-linja."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "nyheter|okonomi"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "ea5a57d51ffb8e98e2742ebdf696f7a2dd0e06b7a974f03f3abf6de9d5be4482"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2017-07-12T09:05:45.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Fr\u00f8ya videreg\u00e5ende skole har f\u00e5tt en undervisningskonsesjon p\u00e5 780 tonn laks."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article1389135.ece5/ALTERNATES/w980-default/fr%C3%B8ya%20laksenot"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/e1a1090397406323d84329504cd2e0182b50becb.jpg?5965e669"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["Elever f\u00e5r egen laksenot -adressa.no", "Elevene har selv ansvar", "Skal ikke tjene penger", "Kamp om de beste folkene", "Forebyggende for r\u00f8mning", "Vil \u00f8ke elevantallet"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "e1a1090397406323d84329504cd2e0182b50becb"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["\u00f8konomi", "finans", "aksjer", "skatt", "b\u00f8rs", "\u00f8konominyheter"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "\u00f8konomi,finans,aksjer,skatt,b\u00f8rs,\u00f8konominyheter"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["nyheter", "okonomi"]}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "education"}, {"field": "kw-company", "value": "marine harvest"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["drifte anlegget", "videreg\u00e5ende skole", "elever"]}, {"field": "kw-enti